com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Class GraphDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.GraphDecorator

  • public final class GraphDecorator
extends Object
    Helper class that can be used to aid in decorating IModelItems from an IGraph instance.

    This class servers as a factory for lookup decorators for the various items that make up an IGraph. This is a convenience class that obtains the ILookupDecorator from the IGraph's ILookup.lookup(java.lang.Class) and passes that to the various specialized decorator convenience classes like e.g. NodeDecorator.

    See Also:
    getNodeDecorator(), NodeDecorator, getEdgeDecorator(), EdgeDecorator, getLabelDecorator(), LabelDecorator, getPortDecorator(), PortDecorator, getBendDecorator(), BendDecorator
